channel.title: How Do You Make A Log In Limit
channel.description: Hello I need help with the amount some1 can log in from 1 ip, now in the config it says 2 are allowed and thats what i changed it to, but when i make multiple accounts it doesnt stop me from getting the starter pack I can get the starter pack everytime no matter how many accounts i make, how do i fix that. I am using a 317 source that is Project Insanity

item.title: How Do You Make A Log In Limit
item.dc:creator: @tgm_clan tgm clan
item.description:
@tgm_clan wrote:

The part that you changed in the config says something like “that can be on at one time” so what you really changed is how many people from the same ip can be on. (that really pisses of brothers that live together lol)

Read full topic
